title: Piped Out by Gallagher
description:
The boys riff on doing ayahausca, taking zoom calls at the zen retreat,  and how saltwater is real bad for phones. They also realize that  stand-up comedy was WILD in the 80's and hear from a listener that had an unfortunate catfishing incident. 

Hear the full episode AND watch the boys literally blow up the Yaris (video out now!) for $5/month on Patreon. You also get instant access to 140 eps in the Patreon back catalog + the stiff socks discord and more. https://www.patreon.com/stiffsockspod
